Jennifer Aniston, 53, has shared a heartwarming Instagram post wishing her good friend Reese Witherspoon a happy 46th birthday. The carousel, posted in view of Jennifer’s 40 million followers, featured a series of old and recent pictures of the pair, as well as a video. The first snap dated back to the time Reese featured in Friends as Jill Greene - Jennifer’s character Rachel's youngest sister. Jennifer also uploaded a clip of the two friends on the set of The Morning Show, with Reese smiling as she waved to the camera. The heartfelt caption read: “It’s somebody’s birthday today. “My little sister [pointing finger emoji] co-anchor [pointing finger emoji] partner in crime. “I LOVE YOU, you sweet ray of sunshine. Let the love pour in! Happy BIRTHDAY @reesewitherspoon”.